                     William Anderson Rose, Esq.; 


                     William Lawrence Esq.; William Ferneley Allen, Esq.; and Edward Conder, Esq.; Aldermen of the said City; 


                     Thomas Chambers, Esq. Common Serjeant of the said City; and Robert Malcolm Kerr, Esq. Judge of the Sheriff's Court of the said City; Her Majesty's Justices of Oyer and Ter
miner and General Gaol Delivery of Newgate, holden for the said City, and Judges of the Central Criminal Court.
